comment: Represents running sums for dns and connect average error counts and average latencies.

variables.name: dnsErrorRate
variables.comment: DNS error rate measured in percentage points.

variables.name: connectLatencies
variables.comment: Blocking connect latencies measured in milliseconds.

variables.name: connectErrorRate
variables.comment: Blocking and non blocking connect error rate measured in percentage points.

variables.name: tcpLossRate
variables.comment: TCP socket packet loss stats collected from Netlink sock_diag.

variables.name: roundTripTimeUs
variables.comment: TCP averaged microsecond round-trip-time stats collected from Netlink sock_diag.

variables.name: sentAckTimeDiffenceMs
variables.comment: differences between last packet sent timestamp and last ack received timestamp.
